pageContext.claim: “Nancy Pelosi just said that she is interested in lowering prescription drug prices & working on the desperately needed USMCA. She is incapable of working on either. It is just camouflage for trying to win an election through impeachment. The Do Nothing Democrats are stuck in mud!”
pageContext.analysis: The House of Representatives has passed dozens of bills, most of which died in the GOP-controlled Senate. Pelosi has made clear her interest in passing the revised version of the North American Free Trade Agreement once agreement could be reached within the Congress on certain elements.
